OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773933104
OL,3,C'Disgusting': Greens' Polanski slams
OL,4,CPM's drug comments in economic speech
OL,6,FGreen Party leader Zack Polanski has
OL,7,Fsaid the prime minister's attacks on
OL,8,Fhim over his recreational drugs policy
OL,9,Fwere "disgusting".
OL,11,FThe London Assembly member wants to
OL,12,Flegalise all recreational drugs if his
OL,13,Fparty won power in a bid to turn their
OL,14,Fuse into a public health issue, rather
OL,15,Fthan criminalising people who fall
OL,16,Finto addiction.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773933104
OL,3,C'Disgusting': Greens' Polanski slams
OL,4,CPM's drug comments in economic speech
OL,6,FBut Prime Minister Keir Starmer has
OL,7,Frepeatedly criticised the policy,
OL,8,Fsaying the idea his teenage son would
OL,9,Fbe able to legally buy heroin is
OL,10,F"disgusting".
OL,12,FHe also accused the rival party of
OL,13,Fbeing "high on drugs, soft on Putin"
OL,14,Fduring a recent Prime Minister's
OL,15,FQuestions.
OL,17,FPolanski hit back at the PM when
OL,18,Ftaking questions after delivering his
OL,19,Ffirst major economic speech as Green
OL,20,FParty leader at a plant nursery in
OL,21,FNorth London.
OL,26,@uD@GOUuD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773933104
OL,3,C'Disgusting': Greens' Polanski slams
OL,4,CPM's drug comments in economic speech
OL,6,FPolanski said: "I think the Prime
OL,7,FMinister's comments were disgusting.
OL,8,FDrug deaths have increased every
OL,9,Fsingle year in this country for the
OL,10,Flast 13 years, we have the highest
OL,11,Fdrug death rate in Europe.
OL,13,F"So the very least I would expect from
OL,14,Fa prime minister or any serious
OL,15,Fpolitician when they're talking about
OL,16,Fdrugs is to recognise that we have a
OL,17,Fpublic health crisis and that should
OL,18,Fbe spoken about with dignity, with
OL,19,Fsensitivity and with care.
OL,26,@nD@POUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773933104
OL,3,C'Disgusting': Greens' Polanski slams
OL,4,CPM's drug comments in economic speech
OL,6,F"What we got from the prime minister
OL,7,Fis cheap political attacks to try and
OL,8,Fwin the Gorton and Denton by-election.
OL,9,FYou'll probably have noticed that we
OL,10,Fstill won with a 4,000 majority, so
OL,11,Fthose political attacks don't work.
OL,13,F"But more seriously, they debase the
OL,14,Fconversation we need to have about
OL,15,Fharm reduction and about speaking to
OL,16,Fpublic health professionals to make
OL,17,Fsure they're involved in that
OL,18,Fconversation."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773933104
OL,3,C'Disgusting': Greens' Polanski slams
OL,4,CPM's drug comments in economic speech
OL,6,FAsked by ITV News how his policy to
OL,7,Flegalise cannabis would impact the
OL,8,Feconomy, he said the fact that
OL,9,FChancellor Rachel Reeves won't even
OL,10,Fconsider the idea as a way to raise
OL,11,Fcash through taxation "demonstrates
OL,12,Fhow distant this government are, from
OL,13,Fthe serious conversations and the
OL,14,Fplans that need to happen".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
