OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773933104
OL,3,C'Disgusting': Greens' Polanski slams
OL,4,CPM's drug comments in economic speech
OL,6,FSetting out his economic stalls more
OL,7,Fwidely, the party leader said the
OL,8,Fgovernment must reverse "decades of
OL,9,Ffiscal tightening, often to meet
OL,10,Ffiscal rules", which have meant
OL,11,F"stretched services, and people
OL,12,Fsuffering".
OL,14,F"Successive governments have hemmed
OL,15,Fthemselves in with an economics that
OL,16,Fdenies people the services they
OL,17,Frequire and support they rely on,
OL,18,Foften to placate a set of arbitrary
OL,19,Frules," he said in his speech at the
OL,20,Ftraditionally Labour-aligned New
OL,21,FEconomics Foundation on Wednesday.
OL,26,@pD@YOUtD@JO]vD@AOU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773933104
OL,3,C'Disgusting': Greens' Polanski slams
OL,4,CPM's drug comments in economic speech
OL,6,F"It is ridiculous, and we need to
OL,7,Fthink again."
OL,9,FHe said "rigid" fiscal multiplier
OL,10,Fassumptions should be updated, as they
OL,11,F"constrain effective government
OL,12,Fpolicy" by "prioritising short-term
OL,13,Ffiscal targets over the longer-term
OL,14,Feconomic and social gains that
OL,15,Ftargeted government spending could
OL,16,Fachieve", holding back planning for
OL,17,Fmajor infrastructure projects and
OL,18,Finvestment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@MO]qD@IOUqD@OO]sD@AOUtD@GO]tD@
OL,26,ALOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
