OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773933104
OL,3,C'Disgusting': Greens' Polanski slams
OL,4,CPM's drug comments in economic speech
OL,6,FPolanski continued: "The government
OL,7,Fshould change these failing fiscal
OL,8,Frules ` opting instead for fiscal
OL,9,Freferees.
OL,11,F"This is a panel of experts tasked
OL,12,Fwith judging debt sustainability,
OL,13,Fwhich includes not only making sure
OL,14,Fthe government is not spending too
OL,15,Fmuch but also ensuring that it isn't
OL,16,Fspending too little."
OL,18,FThe Green leader also said "we need to
OL,19,Flook again at" the Office for Budget
OL,20,FResponsibility (OBR), the government's
OL,21,Fofficial forecaster.
OL,26,@nD@UOUsD@AOUxD@UO]zD@\OU{D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
