OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773933104
OL,3,C'Disgusting': Greens' Polanski slams
OL,4,CPM's drug comments in economic speech
OL,6,F"It was born of promises to
OL,7,F'eliminate' the deficit and take
OL,8,F'urgent action to reduce debt' ` and
OL,9,Fit's clearly failed," he said.
OL,11,FPolanski also detailed his party's
OL,12,Fplans for a wealth tax, "so the super
OL,13,Frich pay their share".
OL,15,FHe said: "We know that a wealth tax
OL,16,Fwon't fix everything, and no one's
OL,17,Fever pretended it would, but it's a
OL,18,Fgood place to start.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@UO]tD@YOUuD@UO]wD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773933104
OL,3,C'Disgusting': Greens' Polanski slams
OL,4,CPM's drug comments in economic speech
OL,6,F"Implementing a 1% tax on wealth over
OL,7,F#10 million and 2% over #1 billion
OL,8,Fwould raise around #15 billion per
OL,9,Fyear ` and send a very clear message
OL,10,Fthat those who have accumulated the
OL,11,Fmost money will pay a little bit more
OL,12,F` and get that money flowing through
OL,13,Fthe economy and benefiting everyone.
OL,15,F"For a truly progressive government a
OL,16,Fwealth tax should be a day one
OL,17,Fpriority."
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
