OL,3,C'Disgusting': Greens' Polanski slams
OL,4,CPM's drug comments in economic speech
OL,6,FHe argued that privatisation and
OL,7,Fderegulation has "turned Britain from
OL,8,Fa place which made things people need,
OL,9,Fto a place which made money for people
OL,10,Fwho owned things".
