OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773933104
OL,3,C'Disgusting': Greens' Polanski slams
OL,4,CPM's drug comments in economic speech
OL,6,FUK billionaires are making money not
OL,7,Ffrom productive economic activity but
OL,8,Ffrom "sitting on assets or charging
OL,9,Fsomebody else for the use of them", he
OL,10,Fsaid, adding: "It's clear that we've
OL,11,Frewarded greed and punished compassion
OL,12,Ffor too long."
OL,14,FHis wealth tax policy has been roundly
OL,15,Fcriticised by the likes of Reform UK
OL,16,Fand the Conservatives as something
OL,17,Fwhich would drive the UK's highest
OL,18,Ftaxpayers to leave the country.
OL,26,@pD@FOUqD@bO]rD@OOUtD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
