PN,31713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773933104
OL,3,C'Disgusting': Greens' Polanski slams
OL,4,CPM's drug comments in economic speech
OL,6,FPolanski made the case for cutting
OL,7,Fenergy bills, rent controls and water
OL,8,Fnationalisation as measures to further
OL,9,Fease the cost of living, and for
OL,10,Fequalising capital gains tax with
OL,11,Fincome tax as a way of raising revenue.
OL,13,FHe said these measures would end "rip-
OL,14,Foff Britain: an economy built to
OL,15,Freward the few off the work of the
OL,16,Fmany. A country where people work so
OL,17,Fhard and try to do the right thing but
OL,18,Fstill struggle to afford the basics,
OL,19,Fand people find themselves constantly
OL,20,Fcutting back".
OL,26,@uD@bOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
