PN,31714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773933104
OL,3,C'Disgusting': Greens' Polanski slams
OL,4,CPM's drug comments in economic speech
OL,6,FHe attacked the Labour government for
OL,7,Foverseeing "managed decline", and
OL,8,FNigel Farage's Reform UK, who he said
OL,9,F"would have dragged us into this
OL,10,Fillegal and deeply unpopular war" in
OL,11,FIran.
OL,13,FPolanski, under whose leadership the
OL,14,FGreens have enjoyed a surge in
OL,15,Fsupport, has been dogged by questions
OL,16,Fover his claim to a Sun newspaper
OL,17,Fjournalist in 2013 that hypnosis could
OL,18,Fincrease a woman's breast size.
OL,26,@oD@LOUoD@\O]qD@AOUrD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
