PN,31715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773933104
OL,3,C'Disgusting': Greens' Polanski slams
OL,4,CPM's drug comments in economic speech
OL,6,FHe repeated his apology in the
OL,7,Fquestion-and-answer session after his
OL,8,Fspeech, seeking to move on from the
OL,9,Fissue by saying: "I've apologised
OL,10,Fseveral times, and I think most people
OL,11,Fare interested in how I'm going to
OL,12,Flower bills."
OL,14,FLabour Party chairwoman Anna Turley
OL,15,Fsaid: "Zack Polanski has the wrong
OL,16,Fanswers on the economy. Respected
OL,17,Feconomists have sounded the alarm over
OL,18,Fthe Greens' 'catastrophic' plans to
OL,19,Fprint money, which would hammer
OL,20,Fworking people and their living
OL,21,Fstandards.
OL,26,@qD@ROUtD@MO]wD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
