PN,31716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773933104
OL,3,C'Disgusting': Greens' Polanski slams
OL,4,CPM's drug comments in economic speech
OL,6,F"Polanski attacks Tory austerity now
OL,7,Fbut as a Lib Dem during the coalition
OL,8,Fyears he was a cheerleader for it at
OL,9,Fthe time ` even though it saw public
OL,10,Fservices slashed and people made
OL,11,Fpoorer. You can't trust him.
OL,13,F"This Labour Government has the right
OL,14,Feconomic plan for Britain ` delivering
OL,15,Fstability, investment in
OL,16,Finfrastructure, and higher living
OL,17,Fstandards after years of Tory failure.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
